      "height": "auto",
      "width": "75%",
      "alt": "random_image"}

  %div
    %p.fw-bold.pt-2
      Privacy Policy...
      %button.btn.btn-outline-info.btn-sm{ "style": "--bs-btn-padding-y: .05rem;", "data-bs-toggle": "collapse", "href": "#privacy-text", "role": "button", "aria-expanded": "false", "aria-controls": "privacy-text" }
        + -
  %div.collapse#privacy-text
    %div.card.card-body.bg-light.border-light.text-justify.mb-3
      %ol
        %li
          I do not collect any personal or financial information at this site.
        %li
          I do not do any tracking of user visits to this site nor do I transmit any such data to other sources. I will publish a statement if this policy changes.
        %li
          A cookie is set when you acknowledge the EU cookie policy. Talk about irony.

