  %div
    %p.fw-bold.pt-2
      Acknowledgements...
      %button.btn.btn-outline-info.btn-sm{ "style": "--bs-btn-padding-y: .05rem;", "data-bs-toggle": "collapse", "href": "#about-ack-text", "role": "button", "aria-expanded": "false", "aria-controls": "about-ack-text" }
        + -
  %div.collapse#about-ack-text
    %div.card.card-body.bg-light.border-light.text-justify.mb-3
      %p
        = link_to "Real Men",
          "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Real_Men_Don%27t_Eat_Quiche",
          target: "_blank"
        give credit where credit is due. Thanks to:
      %ul
        %li
          all of my professional colleagues over the past 40 years, who are too numerous to mention. Thanks for your support and for all the happy hours (pun intended).
        %li
          the
          = link_to "Middleman",
            "https://middlemanapp.com/",
            target: "_blank"
          team for putting together a very nice Ruby-based static site generator.
        %li
          I'm no longer a
          = link_to "fan of Twitter", "http://www.thecwlzone.com/blog/why-i-am-leaving-twitter-behind/", target: "_blank"
          (or any social media to be honest), but the
          = link_to "Twitter Bootstrap",
            "https://getbootstrap.com/",
            target: "_blank"
          team has done a great job in building a remarkable CSS styling framework for those of us with no sense of aesthetics. If the site looks good, it's due to Bootstrap.
        %li
          my wife De’Lynne who is a great photographer and artist. All of the images on the site and the oil paintings in the gallery are her creations.

